 calculate ground state energy and\none particle dispersion and gap at high symmetry point. Using this we draw the\nphase boundary between confined and deconfined phase in the $K-J_1$ plane. The\neffect of $J_2$ is also discussed in the resulting phase boundary.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 11 Mar 2018 17:18:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-02"}
