s fully\nautomated. It has been grafted onto the ArT\\'eMiS pipeline, in charge of the\nformatting, calibration and projection of the data, that is described\nelsewhere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Mar 2018 14:02:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 May 2018 14:59:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-25"}
